text:
Highbridge Park: A set of three views showing the former reservoir under demolition. Nos. 1 and 2 are in an eastward direction and shows the water tower silhouetted against the Washington Heights section of the Bronx; No. 3 veering more to the south.

October 30, 1934.
Views 2 & 3:-November 5, 1934.
